  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Song Taaba de Niassan Koura Parboiled Rice Capacity Building</narrative>
  </title>
  <description type="2">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Support the science and practice of food, feed, and fiber production (including forestry, wildlife, fisheries, aquaculture and floriculture) and its relationships to natural resources, processing, marketing, distribution, utilization (including nutrition), and trade.</narrative>
  </description>
  <description type="1">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">This award strives to support the science and practice of food, feed, and fiber production (including forestry, wildlife, fisheries, aquaculture and floriculture) and its relationships to natural resources, processing, marketing, distribution, utilization (including nutrition), and trade. In addition, this award Sector: Rice processing Beneficiaries: 135 women Description: SONG TAABA operates in the Sourou Valley where they work in partnership with two local rice producing cooperatives and an NGO that provides cash advances to the rice producers, who then tur. Sector: Rice processing Beneficiaries: 135 women Description: SONG TAABA operates in the Sourou Valley where they work in partnership with two local rice producing cooperatives and an NGO that provides cash advances to the rice producers, who then turn over their rice to Song Taaba for par-boilin. The NGO purchases the final product from Song Taaba minus the cost of the advance originally provided for the rice paddy to sell under a brand name. Song Taaba women currently lack access to finance to obtain additional paddy, adequate storage facilities for their final parboiled product, and par-boiling equipment to increase their production. The proposed project will enable Song Taaba to improve their infrastructure, provide improved processing equipment, increase the working capital for the purchase of paddy rice, and obtain training to increase their productivity and competitiveness to supply good quality parboiled rice and white rice on demand to their main commercial partner and to other clients..</narrative>
  </description>
  <description type="2">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">To generate rapid, sustained, and broad-based economic growth.</narrative>
  </description>
